## Install & Setup Vite + React + Typescript + Tailwind CSS 3
- npm create vite@latest
- npm install
- npm install -D tailwindcss@^3.4.17 postcss autoprefixer
- npx tailwindcss init -p
- edit tailwing.config.js and css file

https://larainfo.com/blogs/install-setup-vite-react-typescript-tailwind-css-3/
https://www.alsacreations.com/article/lire/1903-Qu-est-ce-que-Vite.html
https://medium.com/@amirakhaled2027/typescript-vs-typescript-swc-in-vite-understanding-the-differences-7240e7309ca7

## Create prettier.config.js file
- npm install --save-dev prettier
- npx prettier --check .
- npx prettier --write .


